  "title": "Salamanders: The Omnibus",
  "synopsis": "The complete Tome of Fire trilogy in a single volume, gathering Salamander, Firedrake and Nocturne along with a selection of short stories. On the volcanic world of Nocturne, the Salamanders are a Chapter apart, equal parts smith and warrior. Across these linked tales two rival battle-brothers, the visionary Dak'ir and the proud Tsu'gan, are caught in the unfolding of an ancient prophecy as the renegade Nihilan musters Dragon Warriors, Dark Eldar and Chaos renegades for a war of vengeance. From the hunt for a lost relic, through a desperate rescue in a corsair port, to the final battle for Nocturne itself, this is the full saga of the sons of Vulkan and the price they pay to defend their home.",
